'''''Agony of Christ''''' ni film yo muri [[Gana]] yo muri 2009 iyobowe na Frank Rajah Arase . 

== Umugambi ==
Umusore yahunze umudugudu we kuko umupadiri gakondo yashakaga ko yicwa. Yakijijwe nabakristo bamutoje ubumenyi bw'ubukristo aravuka ubwa kabiri. Yagarutse mu mudugudu we aho basengaga imana nto. Igikorwa cye cyo guhindura abantu bose bo mu mudugudu kuba umukirisitu cyaburijwemo n’umupadiri w’igihugu, wemera ko ibyo bibaho bityo amushora mu ntambara yo mu mwuka. 

